      "writtenOn": "2020-12-21T18:19:51Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I\u0027m not clear as to why we need to distinguish between \"we haven\u0027t computed whether this trace matches any ignore rule\" and \"this trace does not match any ignore rule\".\n\nWhat happens when a trace matches exactly one ignore rule, and the ignore rule is deleted? Is matches_any_ignore_rule set to false, or is it set to null?",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 109,
        "startChar": 10,
        "endLine": 109,
        "endChar": 22
      },
      "revId": "0e65e9cf32aee2cf1f5616a7667d20526c5e26e2",
      "serverId": "5086850b-e599-37d2-8ec8-ff16aeccbf02"
